name: Protogen Eclipse Official Release
description:
Protogen Eclipse - How to Build Protogen


By Downloading you agree to the following licenses
CreativeML Open RAIL-M
Dreamlike License

Seek Art Mega License

Live Demo at Available on Hugging Face

Model Weights thanks to reddit user u/jonesaid

This one requires heavy prompting to control and even with good skills, it is random at times, I've been playing with it for a few days and its giving some remarkable scenes, the attention to detail is beyond and it loves Japanese culture.

Why is this released? Its to research what latent space does, and why it behaves the way it does, taming this beast means better outputs, strong prompt skills are the key to good artworks, this is a great learning model for those seeking a little more out of stable diffusion.

Models included

  • 5% modelshoot-1.0

  • 5% roboDiffusion_v1

  • 5% MoistMix

  • 5% HASDX

  • 5% RPG-v3-Candidate16

  • 5% anythingAndEverything

  • 5% openjourney-v2-unpruned

  • 5% dreamlike-diffusion-1.0

ProtoGen_X7.4 is Protogen Eclipse
